---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Work With Will Harvey | Leadership Growth Consulting"
  description="This isn't a programme you fit around running your business. It's proper work, done inside your actual business, together."
>
  <Nav />

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="bg-white pt-28 pb-20 lg:pt-36 lg:pb-28">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <p class="text-brand uppercase tracking-widest text-xs font-semibold mb-6">Work With Me</p>
      <h1 class="font-serif text-5xl lg:text-6xl text-zinc-900 leading-tight mb-6 max-w-2xl">
        Building a business that works without you carrying everything.
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-zinc-500 max-w-xl leading-relaxed">
        This isn't a programme you fit around running your business. It's real work, done together,
        inside the actual thing.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- THE ENGAGEMENT -->
  <section class="bg-stone-50 py-20 lg:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl text-zinc-900 mb-6">What working together looks like</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            Most of my work starts with a discovery call: a straight conversation about where you
            are, what's getting in the way, and whether working together makes sense.
          </p>
          <p>
            If it does, we go deeper in a strategy session. We map out the real situation, identify
            where the biggest leverage is, and agree on what we're building together.
          </p>
          <p>
            From there, we work weekly. Calls, done-for-you work, and ongoing advisory, whatever
            combination makes most sense for your business.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT WE WORK ON -->
  <section class="bg-white py-20 lg:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl lg:text-4xl text-zinc-900 mb-4">The things we typically tackle</h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-500 text-lg mb-14 max-w-2xl">
        Every business is different. But the issues tend to cluster around the same things.
      </p>

      <div class="space-y-0 divide-y divide-zinc-100">
        <div class="py-10 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div>
            <p class="text-brand text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase mb-3">01</p>
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl text-zinc-900">Sales that don't depend on you</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="lg:col-span-2 text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">
            <p>
              If you're still the best salesperson in the business, or the only one, we fix that.
              We work out what's actually winning you work, build a repeatable process around it,
              and put the right tools in place so new business comes in without you chasing it.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="py-10 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div>
            <p class="text-brand text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase mb-3">02</p>
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl text-zinc-900">Hiring and building a team</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="lg:col-span-2 text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">
            <p>
              Whether it's your first hire or your next one, getting it right matters. We build
              the role properly, find the right person, and set up the onboarding so they can
              actually do the job without you holding their hand indefinitely.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="py-10 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div>
            <p class="text-brand text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase mb-3">03</p>
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl text-zinc-900">Getting things off your plate</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="lg:col-span-2 text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">
            <p>
              We look at where your time is actually going and start moving things off your plate.
              Some things need delegating, some need better systems, some shouldn't exist at all.
              The goal is a business that keeps moving when you step away.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="py-10 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div>
            <p class="text-brand text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase mb-3">04</p>
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl text-zinc-900">Strategic clarity</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="lg:col-span-2 text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">
            <p>
              Once the operational weight starts lifting, the question becomes: what do you
              actually want to build? We work on that too, what the business should look like
              in two or three years, and what decisions need to be made now to get there.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- NOT FOR -->
  <section class="bg-stone-50 py-20 lg:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl text-zinc-900 mb-6">A note on fit</h2>
        <p class="text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          I work with a small number of owners at any one time. It's not a volume game.
        </p>
        <p class="text-zinc-900 font-medium mb-4">This probably isn't the right fit if:</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-zinc-600 mb-8">
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-zinc-300 flex-shrink-0 mt-1">-</span>You're pre-revenue or still validating the business</li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-zinc-300 flex-shrink-0 mt-1">-</span>You want a strategy deck and nothing else</li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-zinc-300 flex-shrink-0 mt-1">-</span>You're looking for someone to do your marketing</li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-zinc-300 flex-shrink-0 mt-1">-</span>You're not ready to change how things work</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-zinc-900 font-medium mb-4">It is the right fit if:</p>
        <p class="text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">
          You've got a real business, real challenges, and you're ready to actually work on fixing them.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- INVESTMENT -->
  <section class="bg-white py-20 lg:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl text-zinc-900 mb-6">Investment</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">
          <p>Engagements are bespoke. The scope and investment depend on what we're building together.</p>
          <p>As a reference point:</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-8 space-y-4">
          <div class="border-l-4 border-brand pl-6 py-1">
            <p class="text-zinc-900 font-medium">Advisory retainers</p>
            <p class="text-zinc-500 text-sm mt-1">Typically from £1,000/month</p>
          </div>
          <div class="border-l-4 border-brand pl-6 py-1">
            <p class="text-zinc-900 font-medium">Full builds</p>
            <p class="text-zinc-500 text-sm mt-1">The deeper work: getting sales running without you, building the team, fixing the systems. Quoted based on scope</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-zinc-500 text-sm mt-8">
          The discovery call is free. If it makes sense to work together, we'll put together a clear
          proposal before you commit to anything.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="bg-zinc-900 py-20 lg:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl text-white mb-6">Start with a conversation</h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-400 text-lg mb-10 leading-relaxed">
        Book a discovery call. We'll talk about where you are, what you're trying to build,
        and whether working together makes sense. No pitch. No pressure.
      </p>
      <a
        href="https://calendly.com/will-leadershipgrowthconsulting/30min"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="inline-block bg-white text-zinc-900 px-8 py-4 font-medium hover:bg-zinc-100 transition-colors"
      >
        Book a discovery call
      </a>
      <p class="text-zinc-500 text-sm mt-6">
        I typically work with 4-6 business owners at a time. Worth reaching out sooner rather than later.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
